text: WOW! Welcome home to this beautiful One story in the heart of Southlake! This charming one owner 4 bedroom home is perfect for family and entertaining with its open light & bright floor plan. Upon entering through the custom iron front door you will find a Formal Dining area and private executive Study. The open Family Room has walls of windows with perfect views to a private backyard oasis and is open to the Kitchen. Adorned with designer lighting, the Kitchen area is a focal point with large island with plenty of seating, walk-in Pantry and charming Breakfast nook area with a banquette, all overlooking the pool area. Retreat to the private Master Bedroom and Spa Bath that has abundant light with views to the pool. A separate private Guest Suite enjoys privacy off its own hallway. The additional 2 Bedrooms are on the opposite side of the home, located near the large Game Room and adjacent Media room with screen and projector. Large Mud and Laundry room just outside the 3 car garage which even has its own motorized lift for storage to the attic above. Step outdoors to enjoy a covered living area automated retractable screens, outdoor heater, built-in gas grill and searing station, beverage fridge & a sink. Sparking pool surrounded by cool decking and also has a child safety fence if needed. This one is a rare find!

text: Gorgeous and immaculately maintained executive home in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Cambridge Place. Thoughtfully designed for the entertainer in mind, this one-of-a-kind custom home provides beautiful light-filled living spaces and one of the more impressive outdoor living experiences youll find. The stunning curb appeal will draw you in to find rich hardwoods, dramatic walls of windows, extensive millwork, and classic updates throughout. The bright and inviting kitchen is the heart of the home, opening seamlessly to the oversized family room with views of the lushly landscaped resort-like backyard. Step outside into the designated covered outdoor dining area that opens to an expansive outdoor living with vaulted ceiling, feature fireplace, built-in kitchen and bar, with plenty of space to host large gatherings in the comfort of a private backyard. Dive into the newly resurfaced sparkling pool with multiple water features, enjoy the large sodded area for play, or pull up a chair to roast marshmallows over the built-in fire-pit. The flexible 4 (optional 5) bedroom floor-plan offers primary suite and executive office down, with three spacious ensuite bedrooms and oversized great room with built in bar up. Who doesnt love a secret room? Two bedrooms offer private access to an additional game room! Unwind in the comfort of your private primary suite with large updated bath with stand-alone tub, marble tile and graciously sized walk-in closet, or tackle a new hobby in the massive Laundry or impressive 4 car garage! Whether you love entertaining or are seeking a private estate to call home, nothing will compete with 713 Sussex, a luxurious retreat, right in the heart of Southlake; walking distance to Town Square, top rated Carroll schools and even Dragon Stadium! With easy access to highways and DFW airport but without the nuisance of road or air traffic noise, this home is perfect for the commuter looking for a peaceful place to unwind. Don't miss this one!

text: Situated on a half acre and conveniently located a few minutes walk from Southlake Town Square, this home has it all. Flanking the entry is the formal living room, which can also serve as an office, as well as the formal dining room. Just past the dining room the main level opens up to the family living with gas fireplace and a wall of windows that allow natural light to pour in (unless the electric window shades are drawn, of course). The eat in kitchen is open to the living space and formal dining, and features all matching Kitchenaid stainless steel appliances, including gas cooktop. Just down the hall are two other secondary bedrooms, as well as two full baths, both complete with new tile to give them a fresh new look. The backyard impresses with covered patio featuring built in gas grill leading out to the pool with rock waterfall and spa with tons of room for entertaining. Mature trees line the back fence line creating a wall of privacy and seclusion that make you feel like you are on vacation year round.

text: Spacious and Sophisticated; this beautifully remodeled home provides you all the updates you've been looking for, with all the space you need! The flexible 4 bedroom floor-plan offers endless opportunities to customize how you live with large bedrooms and an unbelievable 5 living spaces! The open loft could easily become a 5th bedroom, office or gym, as the game room and media offer more than enough space for play. Relax with the comforts of a newer roof, windows, and hvac unit. Landscaping and sod were freshly installed (2025). Too many features to list and so much home to explore, in a neighborhood offering trails, stocked lakes, tennis, basketball & playground. This one is a must see!

text: Luxury living at its finest! This exquisitely remodeled home with breathtaking curb appeal is located within the prestigious guard-gated community of Monticello Estates. The exterior wows with modern limestone, sweeping vines, steel double doors and lush landscaping. The curb appeal invites you in to find sophisticated designer details throughout; hardwood floors, dramatic staircase, modern fireplaces, statement lighting and open concept living spaces. The showpiece kitchen, boasting double islands with leathered quartzite, 48in Thermador range, custom cabinetry, spacious pantry and dry bar with undercounter drawer coolers, seamlessly opens to the family room and outdoor living. Primary suite is a retreat with a spa-inspired bath featuring marble flooring and tile, statement chandelier, and luxurious walk-in closet with custom built-ins and back entry to executive office. Guest suite is located opposite on the first floor and also includes an ensuite. The chefs gourmet kitchen is a culinary dream, featuring top of the line Thermador appliances, two dishwashers, a commercial disposal, and a versatile range with both gas burners and griddle alongside four ovens. An oversized island and a sizable pantry complement the space beautifully, ensuring you have everything you need to host and entertain. The formal living room, office, and study area offer scenic views of the propertys lush landscape and luxury diving pool. Outdoor living is equally grand, with a pristine Pavestone entry, handmade gas lamps, and nearly half an acre to design your perfect outdoor haven or cabana. The homes prime location offers easy access to exceptional local schooling, with Old Union Elementary, Eubanks Intermediate School, and Dawson Middle School within walking distance. Enjoy a splendid array of nearby amenities, including generous parks and playgrounds, prestigious shopping at Southlake Town Square, and effortless commuting options to major destinations. Grant yourself the lifestyle you deserve in this serene and opulent Southlake home, where comfort meets quintessential luxury. Whether you're hosting lavish parties or enjoying quiet evenings by the pool, this home invites you to live remarkably.
